---
layout: base
title: FlightFree UK
---

<div class="text-white bg-cover bg-right-top pb-12" style="background-image: url(/images/clouds.png)">
  <%= partial "header" %>
  <section class="xl:flex mt-6 xl:mt-10 mx-8 xl:mx-40">
    <div class="xl:w-2/3 pr-8">
      <h1 class="text-5xl xl:text-6xl leading-tight mb-16">Make the pledge to be flight free in 2020</h1>
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:mb-8 text-orange">#flightfree2020</h2>
      <div class="flex">
        <a href="#" class="w-12 h-12 xl:w-16 xl:h-16 mr-8 bg-white bg-no-repeat bg-center rounded-full" style="background-image:url(svg/twitter.svg);background-size:60%"></a>
        <a href="#" class="w-12 h-12 xl:w-16 xl:h-16 mr-8 bg-white bg-no-repeat bg-center rounded-full" style="background-image:url(images/instagram.png);background-size:60%"></a>
        <a href="#" class="w-12 h-12 xl:w-16 xl:h-16 mr-8 bg-white bg-no-repeat bg-center rounded-full" style="background-image:url(svg/facebook.svg);background-size:30%"></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="xl:w-1/3">
      <button class="bg-orange text-blue-dark text-lg mt-10 mb-8 w-full py-4 xl:hidden" data-micromodal-trigger="pledge-modal">Sign the pledge</button>
      <iframe src="https://services.wedonthavetime.org/campaign/kzsAyW1/" class="hidden xl:block w-full" style="min-height:430px"></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
<section class="xl:flex px-8 xl:px-20 pt-10 pb-16 xl:py-24 bg-blue">
  <div class="xl:w-1/2 mb-10 xl:mb-0">
    <img src="images/anna_with_poster.png" />
  </div>
  <div class="xl:w-1/2 xl:pl-8 xl:pr-24 text-white text-xl xl:text-2xl">
    <h2 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl mb-4 xl:mb-6">Why flight free?</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 xl:mb-6 leading-tight">In 2016 airlines carried 3.7 billion passengers. This is set to rise to more than 7 billion by 2035. At the same time, climate scientists are warning that we have less than 12 years to make a significant reduction in our carbon emissions in order to avoid catastrophic climate change.</p>
    <p class="mb-8 xl:mb-6 leading-tight">We must act now to take meaningful action in order to preserve the planet, and all who rely on it for their survival.</p>
    <a href="#" class="text-orange bg-contain bg-no-repeat bg-right pr-12 py-1" style="background-image:url(svg/orange_arrow_right.svg)">
      More about the campaign
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="bg-orange px-8 xl:px-48 pt-10 pb-6 xl:pt-24 xl:pb-10">
  <h2 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl text-blue-dark mb-8">Take action now</h2>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap">
    <div class="xl:w-1/3 xl:pr-8 mb-10">
      <div class="bg-orange-shadow" style="transform: rotate(4deg)">
        <div class="bg-white border-gray-300 border-4 pt-8 pb-4 px-12 text-center flex flex-wrap justify-center" style="transform: rotate(-4deg)">
          <img src="svg/one.svg" />
          <h3 class="w-full text-3xl text-blue-dark m-6 leading-tight">Sign the pledge</h3>
          <p class="w-full text-2xl mb-12 leading-tight">Help us reach 100,000!</p>
          <button class="w-full bg-blue-dark text-white text-xl uppercase py-4" data-micromodal-trigger="pledge-modal">Pledge now</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="xl:w-1/3 xl:px-4 mb-10">
      <div class="bg-orange-shadow" style="transform: rotate(-4deg)">
        <div class="bg-white border-gray-300 border-4 pt-6 pb-4 px-8 text-center flex flex-wrap justify-center" style="transform: rotate(4deg)">
          <img src="svg/two.svg" />
          <h3 class="w-full text-3xl text-blue-dark m-6 leading-tight">Share the pledge</h3>
          <p class="w-full text-2xl mb-12 leading-tight">Text here about sharing the pledge</p>
          <div class="flex justify-between w-full">
            <a href="#">
              <img src="svg/twitter_with_bg.svg">
            </a>
            <a href="#">
              <img src="images/instagram_with_bg.png">
            </a>
            <a href="#">
              <img src="svg/facebook_with_bg.svg">
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="xl:w-1/3 xl:pl-8 mb-10">
      <div class="bg-orange-shadow" style="transform: rotate(4deg)">
        <div class="bg-white border-gray-300 border-4 pt-6 pb-4 px-12 text-center flex flex-wrap justify-center" style="transform: rotate(-4deg)">
          <img src="svg/three.svg" />
          <h3 class="w-full text-3xl text-blue-dark m-6 leading-tight">Tell us your story</h3>
          <p class="w-full text-2xl mb-12 leading-tight">Text here share your story.</p>
          <button class="w-full bg-blue-dark text-white text-xl uppercase py-4">Write story</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="px-8 pt-16 pb-8 xl:px-48 xl:pt-24 xl:pb-20 bg-gray-light">
  <h2 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl text-blue-dark mb-2 xl:mb-0">Be inspired</h2>
  <h3 class="text-xl xl:text-2xl text-blue mb-8 xl:mb-12 leading-tight">Be inspired by tales of flight-free travels with our blog, podcasts and videos.</h3>
  <section class="xl:flex items-center bg-blue-dark mb-6 xl:mb-12">
    <% podcast = data.podcasts.values.sort_by(&:date).reverse.first %>
    <a href="<%= podcast.url %>" target="_blank" class="block h-40 w-full xl:w-56 bg-no-repeat bg-cover bg-top" style="background-image:url(<%= podcast.cover_image %>" %></a>
    <div class="text-white pt-8 pb-4 xl:py-6 px-8 xl:px-10 xl:w-1/3">
      <a href="<%= podcast.url %>" target="_blank" class="block text-lg xl:text-xl pl-10 mb-4 bg-no-repeat bg-contain" style="background-image:url(svg/podcast.svg)">Listen now</a>
      <a href="<%= podcast.url %>" target="_blank" class="block text-xl xl:text-2xl leading-none">
        <%= podcast.title %>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="xl:flex-grow xl:flex items-center justify-end px-8 xl:pl-0 xl:pr-12 pb-6 xl:pb-0">
      <a href="/podcast.html" class="text-base xl:text-2xl text-orange bg-no-repeat bg-right bg-contain py-1 pr-10 xl:pr-16" style="background-image:url(svg/orange_arrow_right.svg)">
        View all podcasts
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap xl:flex-no-wrap">
      <div class="xl:w-1/3 xl:mr-6 mb-8 bg-white text-blue-dark">
        <%= partial "home_blog_post", locals: { article: blog.articles[0] } %>
      </div>
      <div class="xl:w-1/3 xl:mx-3 mb-8 bg-white text-blue-dark">
        <%= partial "home_blog_post", locals: { article: blog.articles[1] } %>
      </div>
      <div class="xl:w-1/3 xl:ml-6 mb-8 bg-white text-blue-dark">
        <%= partial "home_blog_post", locals: { article: blog.articles[2] } %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="xl:text-right">
      <a href="be_inspired.html" class="text-l xl:text-2xl text-orange bg-no-repeat bg-right bg-contain py-1 pr-10 xl:pr-16" style="background-image:url(svg/orange_arrow_right.svg)">
        View all posts
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</section>
<section class="px-8 pt-12 xl:px-48 xl:pt-24 pb-16 xl:pb-20 bg-blue-dark">
  <h2 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl text-white mb-10">Dispell the myths</h2>
  <div class="border border-white mb-12 xl:mb-20" style="transform: rotate(-4deg)">
    <div class="bg-white px-4 xl:px-48 pt-6 xl:pt-12 pb-8 text-center" style="transform: rotate(4deg)">
      <div class="text-xl text-blue-dark mb-4 xl:mb-8">1 of 3</div>
      <h3 class="text-4xl text-blue mb-8 xl:mb-10 leading-tight xl:leading-snug">“I’m Vegan. That has a bigger impact than giving up flying.”</h3>
      <button class="bg-blue-dark text-xl text-white uppercase py-6 px-8 xl:px-20 mr-3">True</button>
      <button class="bg-blue-dark text-xl text-white uppercase py-6 px-8 xl:px-20">False</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a href="faq.html" class="text-xl xl:text-2xl text-orange bg-no-repeat bg-right bg-contain py-1 pr-12 xl:pr-16" style="background-image:url(svg/orange_arrow_right.svg)">
    Find out more in our FAQs
  </a>
</section>
<section class="px-8 xl:px-48 pt-12 xl:pt-24 pb-12 bg-white">
  <h2 class="text-4xl xl:text-5xl text-blue-dark mb-10">#flightfree2020</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between">
    <img src="images/instagram_photo_1.png" class="mb-8" />
    <img src="images/instagram_photo_2.png" class="mb-8" />
    <img src="images/instagram_photo_3.png" class="mb-8" />
    <img src="images/instagram_photo_4.png" class="mb-8" />
    <img src="images/instagram_photo_1.png" class="mb-8" />
    <img src="images/instagram_photo_2.png" class="mb-8" />
    <img src="images/instagram_photo_3.png" class="mb-8" />
    <img src="images/instagram_photo_4.png" class="mb-8" />
    <img src="images/instagram_photo_1.png" class="mb-8" />
  </div>
</section>
